itle%22%3A%22Nvidia%20just%20blew%20its%20results%20out%20of%20the%20water%20thanks%20to%20a%20technology%20spending%20wave%20that%20analysts%20haven't%20seen%20'since%20the%20internet%20in%201995'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jensen%20Huang%2C%20CEO%20of%20NVIDIA%2C%20holding%20a%20chip.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e67ca84a32f30019748e72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJensen%20Huang%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Nvidia%2C%20the%20chip%20company%20that%20just%20recorded%20record%20revenue.%3Cp%3ESam%20Yeh%20%2F%20Contributor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20announced%20record%20revenue%20of%20%2413.51%20billion.%C2%A0%20for%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%202024%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20chip%20company%20counts%20almost%20every%20major%20tech%20company%20as%20a%20client%2C%20including%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Oracle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnalysts%20are%20calling%20the%20company's%20results%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3B1995%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20evoking%20the%20internet's%20boom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%2C%20the%20leading%20company%20behind%20GPU%20chips%20used%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20software%2C%20announced%20groundbreaking%20revenue%20for%20its%20second%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20even%20stronger%20forecast%20than%20expected%20for%20the%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earnings%20call%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20company%2C%20known%20for%20designing%20graphics%20hardware%2C%20said%20its%20quarterly%20revenue%20was%20%2413.51%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20up%2088%25%20from%20the%20previous%20quarter%20and%20up%20101%25%20from%20one%20year%20ago.%20The%20enormous%20revenue%20reflects%20an%20increase%20in%20AI%20spending%20from%20Nvidia's%20largest%20clients%2C%20such%20as%20Google%20Cloud%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Oracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20Nvidia%20expects%20to%20have%20a%20revenue%20of%20about%20%2416%20billion%2C%20well%20over%20Bernstein%20analysts'%20estimate%20of%20%2411.35%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20results%2C%20while%20impressive%20on%20their%20own%2C%20have%20larger%20implications%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20Gold%20Rush%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20analysts%20from%20Wedbush%20Securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedbush%20referred%20to%20the%20AI%20industry%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B1995%20Moment%20and%20not%201999%2F2000%2C%26quot%3B%20referencing%20the%20year%20that%20interest%20in%20the%20Internet%20exploded%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20years%20that%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20of%20the%20late%2020th%20century%20burst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20earnings%20are%20a%20sign%20that%20AI%20spending%20isn't%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20estimates%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idc.com%2Fgetdoc.jsp%3FcontainerId%3DprUS50454123%26utm_medium%3Drss_feed%26utm_source%3Dalert%26utm_campaign%3Drss_syndication%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Data%20Corporation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spending%20on%20AI%20will%20grow%20by%2027%25%20on%20average%20every%20year%20between%202022%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20build%20out%20is%20unlike%20anything%20we%20have%20seen%20since%20the%20Internet%20in%201995%20and%20the%20ramifications%20are%20just%20starting%20to%20ripple%20through%20the%20consumer%2Fenterprise%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20Wedbush%20analysts%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowth%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20grew%20an%20average%20of%2024%25%20per%20year%20from%201995%20to%202000%2C%20but%20dropped%20sharply%20in%202001%20and%202002%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frbsf.org%2Feconomic-research%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F4%2Fer19-34bk.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Mark%20Doms%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20the%20Federal%20Rese