0lunar%20surface%20today%20and%20the%20rover%20Pragyan%2C%20which%20will%20be%20gathering%20data%20and%20conducting%20experiments%2C%20has%20also%20been%20rolled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hadfield%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20these%20were%20only%20preliminaries.%20%26quot%3BJust%20a%20door%20being%20safely%20opened%20for%20everything%20we%20can%20set%20out%20to%20try%20and%20discover%20on%20the%20moon...%20now%20the%20real%20work%20starts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20water%20molecules%20in%20the%20air%20in%20moon's%20South%20Pole%20by%20a%20NASA%20instrument%20on%20Chandrayaan-1%20in%202009%20had%20given%20rise%20to%20great%20excitement%20in%20anticipation%20of%20future%20moon%20missions.%20Not%20only%20can%20it%20provide%20water%20for%20drinking%20but%20also%20be%20broken%20down%20to%20create%20an%20oxygen%20pool%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%20for%20future%20expeditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Hadfield%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20Vikram%20lander%20have%20landed%20in%20the%20south%2C%2070%20degrees%20south.%20On%20Earth%20it%20would%20have%20been%20on%20the%20shore%20of%20Antarctica.%20That's%20how%20far%20south%20they%20are.%20In%20the%20shadows%20of%20the%20moon%20that's%20where%20the%20water%20can%20stay%20permanently%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20never%20been%20to%20this%20part%20of%20the%20moon...%20So%20the%20opportunity%20of%20discovery%20is%20very%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20mission%20gives%20us%20a%20little%20more%20information...%20It%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20what%20India%2C%20the%20Indian%20people%20and%20(space%20agency)%20ISRO%20chooses%20to%20do%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20India's%20next%20target%20should%20be%20building%20a%20space%20station%2C%20Mr%20Hadfield%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20commander%20of%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20said%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20country's%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20goals%2C%20he%20said%2C%20could%20be%20building%20a%20spaceship%20and%20sending%20its%20own%20citizens%20to%20space%2C%20collaborating%20with%20the%20Artemis%20Space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chief%20S%20Somnath%2C%20in%20the%20euphoric%20moments%20after%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20landing%2C%20said%20India's%20next%20goal%20is%20Gaganyaan%20--%20sending%20a%20man%20into%20space.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20targeting%20to%20have%20it%20on%20September%20or%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pragyan%20Rover%20will%20collect%20information%20for%20the%20next%2014%20days%20%E2%80%93%20equal%20to%20one%20moon%20day.%20As%20the%20night%20on%20the%20moon%20begins%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20equipment%20is%20likely%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692815280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fhgfj12vc_chris-hadfield-_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnow-the-real-work-starts-canadian-astronaut-after-rover-rollout-on-moon-4324033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%3A%20Chris%20Hadfield%2C%20the%20first%20Canadian%20astronaut%20to%20walk%20in%20space%2C%20today%20said%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20possibility%20of%20India's%20moon%20mission%20finding%20crucial%20information%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20water%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnow-the-real-work-starts-canadian-astronaut-after-rover-rollout-on-moon-4324033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnow-the-real-work-starts-canadian-astronaut-after-rover-rollout-on-moon-4324033%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%