0since%20September%202022.%20We%20will%20remain%20watchful%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20raised%20rates%20by%20a%20total%20of%20250%20basis%20points%20since%20May%202022%20to%20tame%20rising%20prices.%20The%20central%20bank%20remains%20firmly%20focused%20on%20aligning%20inflation%20to%20the%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee's%20mandated%20medium-term%20target%20of%204%25%2C%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20price%20stability%20has%20to%20be%20the%20basis%20of%20sustainable%20growth%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20conditions%20are%20favourable%20for%20the%20growth%20to%20continue%20and%20the%20capex%20cycle%20to%20gain%20momentum%20in%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20rupee%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20chief%20reiterated%20that%20the%20RBI%20has%20no%20specific%20target%20but%20would%20continue%20to%20build%20its%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20to%20help%20manage%20any%20dollar%20outflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20has%20also%20made%20conscious%20efforts%20to%20improve%20systemic%20resilience%20and%20efficiency%20by%20maintaining%20external%20stability%20and%20building%20forex%20reserves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692815160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fj0tsf82s_shaktikanta-das-pti_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvegetable-prices-in-india-likely-to-decline-from-september-rbi-chief-4324025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vegetable%20prices%20in%20India%20have%20begun%20to%20soften%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20decline%20from%20September%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%