s%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20end%20of%20such%20cases%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%20The%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20change%20of%20power%20in%20the%20state%20often%20results%20in%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20prosecution%20being%20obfuscated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SURESHKUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjudiciary-has-become-part-of-an-unholy-alliance-madras-hc-judge%2Farticleshow%2F102995640.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RTI%3A%20Years%20of%20Information%20Disappears%20from%20Union%20Government%20Portal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10140837%2Frti-cic-right-to-information.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20what%20is%20a%20further%20shrinking%20in%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20to%20be%20used%20to%20nurture%20a%20climate%20of%20information%2C%20access%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20country%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20records%20of%20lakhs%20of%20previous%20RTI%20applications%20have%20vanished%20from%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20RTIOnline%20portal.%20An%20activist%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20amounts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremoving%20government%20orders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERTIOnline%20is%20the%20platform%20through%20which%20citizens%20can%20file%20for%20access%20to%20public%20information%20and%20record%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fyears-of-data-goes-missing-from-union-governments-rti-portal%2Farticle67226969.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cviewed%20and%20verified%20samples%20of%20applications%20from%20two%20RTI%20activists%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20had%20their%20entire%20account%20purged%20of%20information%20from%20before%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandra%20Shekhar%20Gaur%2C%20an%20RTI%20activist%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mismatch%20of%20several%20hundreds%20in%20his%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20activist%20and%20columnist%20on%20digital%20issues%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20confirmed%20the%20disappearance.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20RTI%20Online%20portal%20was%20being%20turned%20unusual%20by%20the%20government%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months%20with%20them%20stopping%20new%20registrations%20and%20even%20warning%20of%20deleting%20accounts%20that%20are%20not%20being%20used.%20Now%20All%20the%20RTIs%20filed%20prior%20to%202019%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20server.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20this%20was%20as%20serious%20as%20removing%20government%20orders.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20official%20intimation%20about%20it%20to%20any%20of%20the%20RTI%20portal%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%2C%20which%20administers%20the%20portal%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20query%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20missing%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20senior%20rights%20and%20transparency%20activist%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20extremely%20regressive%20move.%20All%20RTIs%20and%20replies%20should%20have%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20been%20made%20public%2C%20as%20also%20mandated%20by%20the%20DoPT.%20It%20might%20be%20useful%20to%20understand%20if%20they%20have%20been%20deleted%20permanently%20or%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20accessible%20on%20the%20portal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20deletion%20on%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20staggering%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20calculates%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20RTIOnline%20portal%20has%20processed%20over%2058.3%20lakh%20applications%20from%202013%2C%20when%20it%20was%20launched%2C%20to%202022.%20The%20number%20of%20applications%20filed%20has%20been%20growing%20steadily%2C%20with%20over%2012.6%20lakh%20applications%20filed%20in%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20site%20had%20been%20behaving%20sub-optimally%20and%20poorly%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20portal%20has%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eat%20least%20two%20periods%20of%20multiple%20days%E2%80%A6%3Cspan%3E%20lagged%20in%20speed%20and%20performance%2C%20and%20applications%20were%20not%20filed%20with%20authorities%20until%20days%20after%20users%20made%20a%20payment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%20was%20a%20landmark%20law%20in%20India%20that%20empowered%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20demand%20public%20information%20and%20inverted%20the%20relationship%20of%20staid%20bureaucracies%20and%20opaque%20governments%2C%20opening%20them%20up%20to%20scrutiny.%20But%20ever%20since%202014%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20get%20information%20through%20applications%2C%20or%20in%20appeal%2C%20has%20been%20hampered%20by%20an%20air%20of%20unwillingness%20in%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20and%20often%20the%20non-appointment%20of%20Information%20Commissioners%20for%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20passage%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20last%20session%20of%20parliament%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewill%20amount%20to%20amending%20the%20RTI%20Act%20through%20the%20backdoor%2C%20experts%20have%20said.%20The%20Bill%20has%20since%20been%20signed%20into%20law.%20Earlier%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovernment-severely-restricting-rti-act-through-data-bill-ncpri%2Farticle67080300.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20larger%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20justified%20the%20disclosure%20of%20personal%20information.%20Now%2C%20the%20new%20data%20Bill%20prohibits%20government%20agencies%20from%20sharing%20private%20information%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20public%20interest%20it%20may%20entail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692814546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10140837%2Frti-cic-right-to-information.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frti-portal-rtionline-years-of-information-disappears%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Right%20to%20Information%20activists%20confirm%20that%20years%20of%20data%20has%20gone%20missing%20from%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20portal.%20The%20site%20has%20processed%2058.3%20lakh%20applications%20since%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frti-portal-rtionline-years-of-information-disappears%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIncredible%20Moment%26quot%3B%3A%20Sundar%20Pichai%20Congratulates%20India%20On%20Moon%20Mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20has%20joined%20millions%20of%20across%20the%20world%20in%20congratulating%20India%20on%20becoming%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole.%20India%20also%20became%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20soft%20land%20a%20craft%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20an%20incredible%20moment!%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pichai%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongratulations%20to%20ISRO%20for%20the%20successful%20landing%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20the%20Moon%20this%20morning.%20Today%2C%20India%20became%20the%20first%20country%20to%20successfully%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20southern%20polar%20region%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Google%20chief%20executive%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAreas%20near%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole%20is%20seeing%20a%20%26quot%3Bgold%20rush%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20high%20chances%20of%20finding%20large%20amount%20of%20water%20there%2C%20first%20found%20by%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover%20Pragyan%20rolled%20out%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20lander%20Vikram's%20touchdown%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELander%20Vikram's%20touched%20down%20days%20after%20a%20Russian%20probe%20crashed%20in%20the%20same%20region%20and%20four%20years%20since%20the%20previous%20Chandrayaan-2%20attempt%20failed%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20has%20captivated%20public%20attention%20since%20launching%20nearly%20six%20weeks%20ago%20in%20front%20of%20thousands%20of%20cheering%20spectators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20took%20much%20longer%20to%20reach%20the%20Moon%20than%20the%20Apollo%20missions%20in%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%2C%20which%20arrived%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20used%20rockets%20much%20less%20powerful%20than%20the%20ones%20the%20US%20used%20back%20then%2C%20meaning%20the%20probe%20had%20to%20orbit%20the%20Earth%20several%20times%20to%20gain%20speed%20before%20embarking%20on%20its%20month-long%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20detached%20from%20its%20propulsion%20module%20last%20week%20and%20had%20been%20sending%20images%20of%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20since%20entering%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solar-powered%20rover%20Pragyan%20will%20explore%20the%20lunar%20surface%20and%20transmit%20data%20to%20Earth%20over%20its%20two-week%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692814320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fkbng7bqg_sundar-pichai-reuters_625x300_21_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincredible-moment-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-congratulates-india-on-moon-mission-4323981%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20and%20Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20has%20joined%20millions%20of%20across%20the%20world%20in%20congratulating%20India%20on%20becoming%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole.%20India%20also%20became%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20soft%20land%20a%20craft%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincredible-moment-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-congratulates-india-on-moon-mission-4323981%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincredible-moment-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-congratulates-india-on-moon-mission-4323981%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincredible-moment-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-congratulates-india-on-moon-mission-4323981%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battling%20Latin%20American%20Producers%20Sketch%20Out%20Roadmap%20Despite%20Huge%20Market%2C%20Political%20Volatility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692814206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F4-Split-copia-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%