ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66590539.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zelenskiy%20vows%20to%20end%20Russian%20occupation%20of%20Crimea%2C%20defends%20strategy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692809578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102994895%2Cimgsize-21538.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskiy-vows-to-end-russian-occupation-of-crimea-defends-strategy%2Farticleshow%2F102994594.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102994594.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20has%20pledged%20to%20end%20Russia's%20occupation%20of%20Crimea%20and%20dismissed%20criticism%20of%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive.%20Zelenskiy%20stated%20that%20Crimea%2C%20along%20with%20other%20occupied%20territories%2C%20will%20be%20reclaimed%20by%20Ukraine.%20He%20said%20Ukrainian%20troops%20were%20advancing%20in%20the%20counteroffensive%20but%20set%20no%20time%20frame%20for%20retaking%20Crimea%20or%20other%20occupied%20territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskiy-vows-to-end-russian-occupation-of-crimea-defends-strategy%2Farticleshow%2F102994594.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskiy-vows-to-end-russian-occupation-of-crimea-defends-strategy%2Famp_articleshow%2F102994594.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskiy-vows-to-end-russian-occupation-of-crimea-defends-strategy%2Famp_articleshow%2F102994594.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rover%20Pragyan%20Rolls%20Out%20Of%20Chandrayaan-3%20Lander%20Near%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20made%20a%20perfect%20landing%20today%20near%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20The%20next%20big%20manoeuvre%20was%20the%20rolling%20out%20of%20the%20Pragyan%20rover%2C%20which%20will%20send%20data%20from%20the%20spot%20to%20the%20lander%20that%20will%20be%20relayed%20to%20space%20agency%20ISRO.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20the%20rover%2C%20though%2C%20took%20time.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20rover%20cannot%20be%20launched%20till%20the%20dust%20kicked%20up%20by%20the%20touchdown%20of%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20is%20dissipated.%20The%20gravity%20of%20moon%20being%20a%20fraction%20of%20that%20of%20Earth%2C%20dust%20does%20not%20settle%20the%20way%20it%20does%20on%20Earth.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20were%20concerned%20that%20if%20the%20rover%20is%20rolled%20out%20before%20the%20dust%20dissipates%2C%20it%20can%20damage%20the%20cameras%20and%20other%20sensitive%20equipment%20on%20the%20rover.%20It%20was%2C%20however%2C%20quicker%20than%20a%20day%20that%20ISRO%20Chief%20S%20Somnath%20had%20spoken%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rover%20will%20come%20out%20in%20a%20few%20hours.%20Sometimes%20it%20takes%20a%20day%20also...%20Once%20the%20rover%20comes%20out%2C%20it%20will%20do%20two%20experiments%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somnath%20had%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20euphoric%20moments%20after%20the%20landing.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20very%20exciting%20time%20after%20Pragyan's%20entry...%20It%20will%20do%20experiments%20for%2014%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover%20Pragyan%20will%20first%20extend%20its%20solar%20arrays%20and%20roll%20out%20with%20a%20wire%20connected%20to%20the%20lander%20Vikram.%20The%20wire%20will%20be%20snapped%20once%20the%20rover%20is%20stable%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20It%20will%20then%20start%20its%20scientific%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experiments%20will%20continue%20for%2014%20days%20--%20which%20is%20a%20single%20moon%20day.%20As%20the%20night%20on%20the%20moon%20begins%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20equipment%20is%20likely%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20to%20be%20sent%20by%20Pragyan%20is%20of%20vital%20importance%2C%20given%20the%20traces%20of%20water%20found%20in%20the%20area.%20This%20was%20detected%20by%20a%20NASA%20instrument%20aboard%20the%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-1%20probe%20in%202009.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20the%20first%20moon%20mission%20to%20land%20near%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20water%20--%20which%20will%20be%20crucial%20commodity%20in%20view%20of%20future%20moon%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20water%20holds%20hope%20for%20future%20moon%20missions%20--%20it%20could%20be%20used%20as%20a%20source%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20to%20cool%20equipment%20and%20broken%20down%20to%20produce%20oxygen.%20It%20can%20also%20have%20clues%20to%20the%20origins%20of%20oceans.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692808800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcpcemd6k_first-visuals-1200_650x400_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frover-pragyan-rolls-out-of-chandrayaan-3-lander-near-moons-south-pole-4323646%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20made%20a%20perfect%20landing%20today%20near%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20The%20next%20big%20manoeuvre%20was%20the%20rolling%20out%20of%20the%20Pragyan%20rover%2C%20which%20will%20send%20data%20from%20the%20spot%20to%20the%20lander.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A701%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frover-pragyan-rolls-out-of-chandrayaan-3-lander-near-moons-south-pole-4323646%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.nd