econd%20game%20finished%20quite%20quickly%20as%20after%20only%2030%20moves%20the%20players%20decided%20to%20shake%20hands.%20The%20champion%20will%20be%20decided%20via%20two%20tie-breaks%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive-time%20world%20champion%20Carlsen%20played%20a%20solid%20game%20with%20white%20pieces%20against%20Praggnanandhaa.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20did%20not%20face%20any%20trouble%20with%20black%20pieces.%20Indian%20chess%20legend%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20predicted%20on%20social%20media%20that%20Carlsen%20might%20be%20playing%20for%20a%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWow%2C%20did%20not%20expect%20this%20opening!%20Is%20Magnus%20repeating%20his%20game%2012%20strategy%20of%202016%20and%20aiming%20for%20a%20tiebreak%3F%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFIDE_chess%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40FIDE_chess%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FFIDEWorldCup2023%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23FIDEWorldCup2023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20(%40vishy64theking)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvishy64theking%2Fstatus%2F1694306166476874047%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20commentators%20of%20the%20match%2C%20said%20during%20the%20initial%20few%20minutes%20of%20the%20match%20that%20because%20Carlsen%20was%20battling%20with%20food%20poisoning%20was%20not%20in%20the%20right%20frame%20of%20health%20he%20might%20be%20playing%20for%20a%20draw%2C%20which%20would%20take%20the%20final%20to%20the%20third%20day.%20Thus%20giving%20the%20Norwegian%20great%20some%20valuable%20time%20to%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraggnanandhaa%20was%20ahead%20on%20time%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20press%20home%20the%20advantage.%20He%20himself%20came%20under%20time%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20contest.%20The%20first%20game%20on%20Tuesday%20had%20ended%20in%20a%20stalemate%20after%20over%20four%20hours%20of%20play%20and%2070-plus%20moves%2C%20following%20which%20Carlsen%20said%20he%20was%20a%20bit%20under%20the%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20game%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20really%20think%20that%20he%20would%20go%20for%20a%20quick%20draw%20today%2C%20but%20I%20realised%20when%20he%20went%20for%20this%20line%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20draw%3B%20I%20was%20also%20fine%20with%20that.%20I%20also%20feel%20exhausted%2C%20as%20I%20said%20in%20the%20previous%20interviews.%20Now%20I%20can%20just%20give%20everything%20tomorrow%20and%20relax%20after%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20if%20he%20realised%20that%20Carlsen%20was%20under%20the%20weather%20during%20the%20first%20game%2C%20the%20Indian%20player%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah.%20It%20didn't%20feel%20like%20he%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20I%20felt%20that.%20I%20didn't%20think%20he%20was%20unwell.%20I%20hope%20he%20recovers%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20would%20suggest%20to%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20future%20for%20an%20extra%20rest%20day%20before%20the%20final%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20if%20it%20is%20there.%20It%20would%20be%20good.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20media%20attention%20he%20was%20getting%2C%20the%20Indian%20star%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20definitely%20getting%20used%20to%20this.%20It%20is%20good%20to%20see%20so%20many%20people%20following%20chess.%20Chess%20is%20definitely%20getting%20popular%2C%20that%20way%20I%20am%20very%20happy.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20Praggnanandhaa%20has%20been%20enjoying%20an%20incredible%20run%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20having%20already%20beaten%20world%20No.2%20Hikaru%20Nakamura%20and%20world%20No.3%20Fabiano%20Caruana%20to%20set%20up%20a%20final%20date%20against%20the%20Norwegian%20Grandmaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%20also%20helped%20Praggnanandhaa%20qualify%20for%20Candidates%202024%20tournament%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Canada.%20Praggnanandhaa%2C%20thus%2C%20became%20the%20third%20youngest%20player%20after%20the%20legendary%20Bobby%20Fischer%20and%20Carlsen%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Candidates%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20game%2C%20Carlsen%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPraggnanandhaa%20has%20already%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20tie-breaks%20against%20very%20strong%20players...%20I%20know%20he%20is%20very%20strong.%20If%20I%20have%20some%20energy%2C%20if%20I%20have%20a%20good%20day%2C%20obviously%20I%20will%20have%20good%20chances.%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20organisers%2C%20FIDE%20and%20the%20doctors%20and%20nurses%2C%20who%20got%20me%20some%20good%20treatment.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20feeling%20a%20bit%20better%20but%20I%20still%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20had%20the%20energy%20for%20a%20full%20fight%2C%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20let's%20get%20one%20more%20day%20of%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20I%20will%20have%20more%20strength%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Norwegian%20world%20No.1%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20tie-break%20games%20in%20rapid%20format%20will%20be%20played%20with%20a%20time%20control%20of%2025%20minutes%20for%20each%20player%20plus%2010%20seconds%20increment%20per%20move%2C%20starting%20from%20move%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20two%20games%20also%20fail%20to%20throw%20a%20winner%2C%20two%20more%20games%20with%20time%20control%20of%205%20minutes%20for%20each%20player%20will%20be%20played.%20There%20will%20be%203%20seconds%20increment%20per%20move%2C%20starting%20from%20move%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraggnanandhaa%20is%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20after%20the%20legendary%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20to%20reach%20the%20World%20Cup%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692805380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F7vcm59u_praggnanandhaa-carlsen_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmagnus-carlsen-did-not-have-lot-of-energy-praggnanandhaa-after-2nd-drawn-chess-world-cup-final-game-4323473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chess%20World%20Cup%20final%20between%20Indian%20teenager%20R%20Praggnanandhaa%20and%20world%20No.%201%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20went%20into%20the%20tie-breakers%20after%20the%20second%20game%20of%20the%20title%20clash%20ended%20in%20a%20draw%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A405%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmagnus-carlsen-did-not-have-lot-of-energy-praggnanandhaa-after-2nd-drawn-chess-world-cup-final-game-4323473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmagnus-carlsen-did-not-have-lot-of-energy-praggnanandhaa-after-2nd-drawn-chess-world-cup-final-game-4323473%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmagnus-carlsen-did-not-have-lot-of-energy-praggnanandhaa-after-2nd-drawn-chess-world-cup-final-game-4323473%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BProud%20Of%20Them%26quot%3B%3A%20Families%20Of%203%20ISRO%20Scientists%20From%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20dedication%20and%20innovation%20of%20three%20scientists%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20have%20not%20only%20brought%20glory%20to%20the%20country%20but%20have%20also%20added%20a%20new%20chapter%20to%20India's%20space%20exploration%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20the%20cosmos%2C%20humankind's%20insatiable%20curiosity%20continues%20to%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20exploration.%20The%20three%20scientists%20helmed%20each%20of%20the%20crucial%20Moon%20missions%20of%20India's%20space%20programme%2C%20including%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20which%20carried%20the%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20of%20an%20entire%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20Thakre%2C%20a%20scientist%20from%20Maoist-affected%20Balaghat%20district%2C%20is%20the%20project%20manager%20of%20Chandrayaan-3.%20He%20has%20over%2030%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20space%20sector%20and%20has%20worked%20on%20several%20other%20missions%2C%20including%20Chandrayaan-1%20and%20Mangalyaan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20working%20as%20a%20team%20manager%20in%20launching.%20We%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20our%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakre's%20father%20Khusilal%20Thakre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20went%20up%20to%20the%20top%2C%20and%20is%20an%20honour%20for%20our%20village%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20scientist's%20neighbour%20Rameshwar%20Chaudhry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20scientist%2C%20Priyanshu%20Mishra%2C%20is%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20tribal-dominated%20Umaria%20district.%20An%20MTech%20from%20Ranchi%2C%20he%20has%20been%20working%20at%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20scientist%2C%20Om%20Pandey%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Satna%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20team%20monitored%20Chandrayaan's%20orbit%20and%20trajectory.%20He%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20landing%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%20studied%20electrical%20engineering%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Kanpur%20and%20joined%20ISRO%20in%202018.%20His%20mother%2C%20Kusum%20Pandey%2C%20said%20he%20is%20a%20very%20devoted%20son%2C%20adding%20he%20talks%20to%20his%20family%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20neighbours%20are%20asking%20how%20to%20get%20into%20ISRO.%20We%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pandey's%20wife%20Shikha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692805260000%2C%22visual%