n%20the%20series.%20As%20it%20was%2C%20it%20finished%20two%20tests%20a%20piece%20with%20the%20fifth%20drawn%20and%20so%20the%20Aussies%2C%20as%20the%20current%20holders%2C%20retain%20the%20trophy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20290px)%2085vw%2C%20290px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22290%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20World%20Cup%20has%20been%20the%20summer%E2%80%99s%20big%20event%2C%20even%20though%20the%20hosting%20of%20the%20series%20by%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20led%20to%20very%20early%20kick-offs%20British%20time.%20The%20Lionesses%2C%20the%20moniker%20given%20to%20the%20England%20women%2C%20were%20European%20champions%20last%20year.%20Lucy%20Bronze%2C%20Lauren%20James%2C%20Mary%20Earps%20and%20Millie%20Bright%20have%20become%20household%20names.%20And%20in%20Australia%20on%20Sunday%2C%20they%20took%20England%20%E2%80%93%20the%20nation%20which%20likes%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20invented%20all%20the%20main%20team%20sports%20%E2%80%93%20to%20its%20first%20World%20Cup%20final%20for%20almost%2060%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20they%20lost%20%E2%80%93%20by%20the%20only%20goal%20to%20Spain%2C%20who%20were%20the%20deserved%20winners.%20Tears%20were%20shed%20in%20homes%2C%20pubs%2C%20halls%20and%20even%20churches%20across%20the%20country%20where%20fans%20gathered%20at%20eleven%20o%E2%80%99clock%20on%20Sunday%20morning%20to%20watch%20the%20game.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20so%20much%20sweeter%20to%20have%20won%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20team%20famously%20did%20back%20in%201966%2C%20convincing%20a%20tattered%20post-imperial%20nation%20that%20we%20still%20had%20something%20going%20for%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20defeat%20in%20Sydney%20was%20still%20a%20victory%20%E2%80%93%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20sport.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20attracted%20big%20money%20corporate%20sponsorship%20and%20was%20watched%20eagerly%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20play%20was%20flowing%20and%20exciting%20to%20watch.%20Football%2C%20so%20often%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98beautiful%20game%E2%80%99%2C%20lived%20up%20to%20that%20description.%20A%20sport%20which%20has%20so%20often%20been%20vulgar%20and%20sexist%20has%20been%20in%20part%20redeemed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20fully%20half-a-century%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20was%20banned%20in%20England.%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20game%20developed%20in%20the%201880s%2C%20and%20some%20early%20matches%20attracted%20a%20crowd%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands.%20But%20in%201921%20the%20Football%20Association%20outlawed%20the%20use%20of%20any%20of%20its%20grounds%20and%20facilities%20for%20women%20declaring%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20game%20of%20football%20is%20quite%20unsuitable%20for%20females%20and%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20encouraged%E2%80%99.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20football%20withered%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ban%20was%20only%20lifted%20in%201970.%20And%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Super%20League%20%E2%80%93%20the%20top%20tier%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20in%20England%2C%20with%2012%20professional%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20was%20established%20as%20recently%20as%202010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fseven-ways-fifa-world-cup-move-dial-womens-sport%5C%22%3ESeven%20Ways%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20Can%20Move%20the%20Dial%20on%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Sport%20Forever%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAttendances%20at%20women%E2%80%99s%20games%20are%20not%20as%20high%20as%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20Premier%20League%3B%20transfer%20fees%20and%20salaries%20are%20more%20modest.%20But%20that%20is%20starting%20to%20change.%20Arsenal%20now%20stage%20as%20many%20of%20their%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20games%20as%20they%20can%20at%20their%20main%20venue%2C%20the%20Emirates%20stadium%2C%20rather%20than%20their%20training%20ground%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20London%20%E2%80%93%20and%20with%20clever%20marketing%20and%20competitive%20ticket%20pricing%2C%20they%20can%20fill%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20shining%20star%20of%20England%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20performance%20is%20a%2053-year-old%20Dutch%20woman%2C%20Sarina%20Wiegman.%20As%20manager%20of%20the%20England%20team%2C%20she%20took%20the%20Lionesses%20to%20European%20glory%20last%20year%20and%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20this%20year.%20She%20has%20moulded%20a%20talented%20group%20of%20players%20into%20a%20stylish%20team.%20She%20is%20not%20only%20calm%3B%20she%E2%80%99s%20kind.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20something%20you%20can%20say%20of%20many%20football%20managers.%20She%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20master%20tactician%20%E2%80%93%20so%20much%20so%20that%20some%20have%20suggested%20she%20take%20over%20as%20manager%20of%20England%E2%80%99s%20men%E2%80%99s%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESarina%20Wiegman%20has%20coached%20at%20four%20major%20tournaments%20and%20reached%20the%20final%20EVERY%20time%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%96%AA%EF%B8%8F%20Euro%202017%20%F0%9F%87%B3%F0%9F%87%B1%F0%9F%8F%86%3Cbr%3E%E2%96%AA%EF%B8%8F%20World%20Cup%202019%20%F0