e%20suspicion%20of%20meat%20in%20the%20refrigerator%20of%20a%20Muslim%20household%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20need%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98reason%E2%80%99.%20Any%20lunatic%20will%20pick%20up%20a%20gun%20someday%20and%20shoot%20you%20down%20simply%20because%20you%20exist%2C%20and%20one%20will%20only%20be%20left%20fact-checking%20statements%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20contend%20that%20their%20actions%20were%20the%20result%20of%20years%20of%20hatred%20and%20not%20an%20act%20of%20momentary%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20this%20lingering%20fear%20has%20now%20become%20deeply%20ingrained%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20common%20Muslims%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20change%20their%20style%20of%20living%20in%20order%20to%20save%20their%20lives.%20The%20fear%20is%20so%20deep-seated%20that%20almost%20every%20person%20who%20gave%20their%20comments%20for%20this%20report%20did%20so%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah*%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20capital%20city%20Patna%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incidents%20on%20trains%20%5Bprevious%20lynchings%20and%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%5C%22%3Eshootout%20in%20the%20Jaipur-Mumbai%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%20have%20shaken%20me%20to%20the%20core.%20I%20had%20already%20stopped%20carrying%20food%20during%20train%20journeys%2C%20and%20even%20if%20I%20did%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20that%20it%20did%20not%20look%20like%20meat.%20Sometimes%2C%20instead%20of%20having%20a%20proper%20meal%2C%20I%20only%20rely%20on%20snacks%20while%20travelling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F03005229%2FF2YFcpNWwAEWXWa-102