e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20punctuality%20of%20mail%20and%20express%20trains%20has%20decreased%20to%2073%25%20by%20mid-August%20of%20the%20current%20financial%20year%2C%20showing%20an%2011%25%20fall%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(TOI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpassenger-train-punctuality-freight-train-speeds-down%2Farticleshow%2F102921497.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20speed%20of%20freight%20trains%20also%20fell%20to%2027.5%20kmph%2C%20a%20reduction%20from%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%2032.4%20kmph%20while%20the%20total%20freight%20loading%20saw%20a%20marginal%201%25%20increase%2C%20reaching%20558%20million%20tonnes%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERailway%20officials%20attributed%20the%20decline%20to%20increased%20focus%20on%20maintenance%20of%20tracks%20and%20giving%20adequate%20blocks%20for%20carrying%20out%20new%20and%20maintenance%20works.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20compromise%20with%20regard%20to%20ensuring%20proper%20blocks%20for%20taking%20up%20any%20work%20on%20our%20network.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20safety%20and%20asset%20maintenance.%20There%20is%20also%20strict%20adherence%20to%20respecting%20the%20stop%20signals%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20was%20quoted%20by%20TOI%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcover-your-tracks-the-modi-governments-attitude-after-the-balasore-tragedy%5C%22%3ECover%20Your%20Tracks%3A%20The%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Attitude%20After%20the%20Balasore%20Tragedy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20reasons%20for%20decreased%20punctuality%20are%20%E2%80%98asset%20failure%20and%20more%20construction%20works%E2%80%99%2C%20TOI%20reported.%20An%20assessment%20of%20railways%E2%80%99%20train%20operations%20and%20maintenance%20till%20the%20first%20week%20of%20August%20this%20year%20shows%20that%20there%20were%2014%20%E2%80%98consequential%20accidents%E2%80%99%20compared%20to%20six%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsequential%20rail%20accidents%20are%20those%20which%20cause%20loss%20of%20human%20life%2C%20injury%2C%20loss%20of%20railway%20property%20and%20interruption%20to%20rail%20traffic.%20The%20biggest%20consequential%20accident%20took%20place%20on%20June%202%20at%20Bahanaga%20Bazar%20station%20in%20Balasore%20which%20claimed%20294%20lives%20and%20left%20over%201%2C000%20injured%2C%20the%20TOI%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20performance%20details%20also%20show%20that%20track%20failures%20or%20defects%20increased%20by%2010%25%20and%20signal%20failures%20went%20up%20by%2021%25%20between%20April%20and%20mid-August%2C%202023%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692781210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fslow-and-unsteady-punctuality-of-trains-drops-to-73%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20speed%20of%20freight%20trains%20also%20fell%20to%2027.5%20kmph%2C%20a%20reduction%20from%20the%20previous%20year's%2032.4%20kmph.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fslow-and-unsteady-punctuality-of-trains-drops-to-73%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20planes%20cleared%20to%20take%20off%2C%20land%20at%20same%20time%20at%20Delhi%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692780898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2