%20world-map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20to%20all%20adventure%20lovers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-300x285.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-500x474.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-768x729.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-1536x1457.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-150x142.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327706%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20to%20all%20adventure%20lovers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20their%20very%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20of%20hosting%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20say%20it%20was%20New%20Year%E2